{"atom_id":"ig34_p0146_a021","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":146,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.2.2 [Biospecimen Events (BE)]","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"Row 4:\tShows the extraction of the RNA, which includes purification and quality control testing to make sure the sample is of a high enough quality to be viable. BESPDEVID holds the identifier for the purification kit.","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":4,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":"oh-my-claudecode:executor|P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R15+drift_cal_repair"}
